typedef float f32;

// Vector Type
struct Vector3
{
    f32 x, y, z;
};
typedef Vector3 Vector3;

f32 dot3(const Vector3 a, const Vector3 b)
{
    return a.x * b.x + a.y * b.y + a.z * b.z;
}

int main(int argc, char* argv[])
{

    Vector3 v = {1, 4, 9};
    Vector3 c = {2, 0.5f, 0.222f};

    printf("{%.0f, %.0f, %.0f}\n", v.x, v.y, v.z);
    printf("%f\n", sqrtf(dot3(v, c)));
